&lt;p&gt;With 15+ years of experience in Games, XR and Creative Tech, I work on exhibition displays, art installations, videogames and creative software.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I work in Unity, Three.js, WebGPU, and more.&lt;/p&gt;
